CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page A20, reads: "The George E. Drake Baking Company booth with hostesses Betty Fowler and Delores Redwood and officials John W. Guay and W.H. Sharlow."
TitMainTitle: Betty Fowler, John W. Guay, W. H. Sharlow, and Delores Redwood standing in the George E. Drake Baking Company booth in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Courier Home Service Fair
